Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.12,0:24:35.71,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you can\ncome out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.23,0:24:39.24,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! How have you been,\ndumb son o' mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.86,0:24:42.79,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A fool in that position...\nwill cause us trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.54,0:24:44.92,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about a\nself-centered boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.34,0:24:47.19,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But he doesn't know the meaning\nof the word harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.49,0:24:49.35,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And whose fault\nis that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.71,0:24:51.20,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You said it to me once,\nremember?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.41,0:24:55.73,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm a man of exceptional talent who is\nincapable of loving anything but spaceships.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.95,0:24:57.88,Standard (PlanetES),Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your comments to yourself,\nyou sleazy old geezer!
